Author: Sygari
Text: Felt this in my core.. I'm sorry you are feeling so down, I'm here for you if you need me.

Author: idkidkidkidk1515
Text: Its not attention whoring. Do you wanna talk? I am here and I know how it is to feel that way. You're most likely not even fat. My friend was bulimic and I helped her through it and I wanna help you.
